          <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-swatch" style="background:#86efac"></span>低（≤${k(maxUnits * 0.25)} 宅）</div>
          <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-swatch" style="background:#f97316"></span>中（≤${k(maxUnits * 0.5)} 宅）</div>
